              <strong>ZeleeBooks Store </strong>by logging into your QuickHire account. Should there be any
              updates or if further information is required, you will be notified accordingly through your
              account or via email.
            </p>
            <p
              style="
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 24px;
                margin: 16px 0;
                color: rgb(100, 116, 139);
                margin-top: 0px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                text-align: left;
                -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
                -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
              "
            >
              Thank you for using QuickHire to advance your career. We wish you the best of luck with your
              application.
            </p>
            <p
              style="
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 24px;
                margin: 16px 0;
                color: rgb(100, 116, 139);
                margin-top: 0px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                text-align: left;
                -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
                -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
